Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:04.13,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Maison de Ayakashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:07.15,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,also known as Ayakashi Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:10.86,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,A luxury apartment complex, \Ncomplete with bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:16.17,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Secretly, it's a place where humans \Npartially descended from
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:17.95,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,supernatural creatures live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:21.54,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place full of eccentric people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.80,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's also where I met
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.77,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,my Secret Service bodyguard,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:30.13,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Miketsukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:34.89,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that the one I had \Nonce exchanged letters with
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:37.48,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,was him, pretending to be Kagerou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:42.22,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, he explained the \Nsituation and apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:46.18,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he had carefully \Npreserved all my letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:48.19,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But that if I wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:53.14,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,he would return them, as they \Nwere never meant for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:56.35,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I told him he could keep them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:58.87,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Because I had sent them to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:03.04,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Then he gave me one of those smiles, \Nlike he was about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:19.99,Inuboku-internal,Text+Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:20.85,Sign12B,Text+Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,687)}And then, I made up \Nmy mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:31.02,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.04,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorinozuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:34.77,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Are you helping out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:36.90,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need to see your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:37.93,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Go on in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:39.81,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:40.70,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:43.12,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I just stopped by...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:47.96,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorinozuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.96,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this is all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:53.26,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Your cover will be blown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:54.45,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:56.84,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,If people see something they can't process,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:59.22,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,their brain adjusts to it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.17,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Even if someone took a picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:03.60,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,I'd just get coverage during some \Nsummer urban legend special.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:04.89,Sign12A,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Special Report \NFlying Cloth Monster \N\N{\fs20}Who is the boy riding it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:06.73,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,That's so careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.90,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,And here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:13.39,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't transform in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:16.44,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,It's wrong to confuse people just for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:18.53,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:20.93,Inuboku-internal,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,I just got told off by a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:22.64,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:26.81,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,you kinda seemed like you didn't \Nreally want to see your dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:30.04,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,And if you enter through the front, \Nthe lounge is right there,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.80,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,which means you might run into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.42,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorinozuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.41,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:37.30,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,You carry a supernatural creature's blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:39.62,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,like my father does, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:41.55,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.82,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it true that people like you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:48.01,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,have the same personalities, and sometimes even memories, as your ancestors?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:51.06,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,How does that differ from \Nnormal reincarnation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:54.44,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,If my dad dies, will he be reincarnated again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:58.86,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,If he marries a woman who isn't \Nmy mother in his next life,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:01.70,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,will he be the father of \Nsomeone other than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.66,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:06.37,Inuboku-internal,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,I expected this to be a more \Nclear-cut father-son dispute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:09.41,Inuboku-internal,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,This kid thinks about some complicated stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.83,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been \Nthinking about all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.80,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I only just now found out about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.23,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard my father and the others talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:20.25,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I understood what it means to have the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.75,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.69,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you can worry about \Nsomething so far in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:30.96,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even consider what I'm \Ngoing to have for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.90,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's bury a time capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.73,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Both your entrance and your \Ncomment were quite sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:42.55,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so concerned, why not \Nwrite your father a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.99,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,B-But what can a time capsule do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:49.75,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Then your father can read \Nyour letter in his next life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:53.25,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,My father... In his next life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:57.55,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You could write something like, \N"Don't marry anyone but Mom!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:01.76,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Or like, "I'm your only child, Dad!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.68,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:05.93,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:06.93,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.66,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.10,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.28,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's gather all our friends together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:17.94,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you do, you have to \Nhave fun doing it with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.78,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,A time capsule?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.97,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm a delinquent, \Nso don't expect me to go along...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.20,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.82,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write you a letter, Watanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.59,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write a letter for you, in your next life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:31.75,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,But in your next life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.70,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,maybe you won't be friends
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:37.27,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,with me in my next life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:39.38,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,So you wouldn't read my letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:42.64,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.30,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we'll be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.47,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy some stationery!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.17,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:51.11,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,But what will we be in our next lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.23,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.48,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to be a steamed bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.84,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Filled with red bean paste or meat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.12,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,pizza or Belgian chocolate,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:03.12,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,custard or stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:08.03,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Steamed buns are always filled \Nwith wonderful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:13.61,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be filled with \Nwonderful things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:16.42,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, you want to be \Nsomething that gets eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:20.75,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep eating until \Nthe moment I get eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.05,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,This soil is hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.68,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up. Don't make me regret \Nplaying along with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.68,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.26,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.71,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:38.28,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,You know, just looking at us now, \Nwe kinda resemble a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.93,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,He's even got the droopy eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.15,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,RenRen, did you dig the hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.90,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,I just buried him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:49.66,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little late to ask, but do you \Nthink it's okay to dig a hole here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.46,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,It is a shared property.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.45,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Generally, nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.83,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,And will this complex even \Nsurvive for that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.34,Sign12C,Chara,0000,0000,0000,,Death
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.55,Sign12D,Letter,0000,0000,0000,,To My Future Self
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.55,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.06,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:16.27,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Want to join in, Ririchiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.40,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Hah... A time capsule?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.30,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.22,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you ask a high \Nschool student to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:25.60,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.24,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:33.60,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it just happens I already \Nhad my stationery set out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.04,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I could participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.12,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:40.30,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:42.25,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It really was a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:44.96,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I was writing a letter to include \Nwith a box of cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.13,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.86,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, you've really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:52.03,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,When you first got here, you told \Neveryone to leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.36,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,From...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:55.14,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,From?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.81,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,F-From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.53,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,a little interaction
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:04.69,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,with others won't be something \NI'd d-dismiss out of hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:06.69,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,F-For a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:11.58,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably say rude things and \Nmake you guys uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.20,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.54,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty dense, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:21.75,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just don't come crying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.53,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:27.53,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother wants to make a time capsule?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.67,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:32.26,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He said you should participate, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:36.00,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,And this... Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:39.26,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Because I dropped that melon I got you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:41.73,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But don't expect anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.40,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You did not need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.10,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And the melon from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:48.90,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I preserved it, to keep it fresh, \Nand I have safely stored it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.53,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't. Just eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:53.38,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,When did you manage to get this, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:56.30,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I just picked it up during my lunch hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.26,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.16,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You exposed yourself to such danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.75,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.56,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I shall treasure it always.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.67,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I said to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.82,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm going to the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:09.98,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,To the garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:13.20,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You're participating in the \Ntime capsule project?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.15,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why? Is there something wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.94,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Are they forcing you to take part again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:19.43,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:22.83,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.98,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for acting out of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:26.95,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:31.01,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you go down to the garden \Nand wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.19,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I shall participate, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.79,Inuboku-flashback,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You really should interact \Nmore with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:44.83,Inuboku-flashback,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,That's a skill that can only be learned by
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.48,Inuboku-flashback,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,hurting and being hurt by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.51,Inuboku-flashback,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,You've really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:53.34,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, given that I \Ncame here to be alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:58.68,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But meeting these people has
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.72,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,made me want to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:05.85,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Since I met him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:08.31,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.77,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I may hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.44,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,And I may get hurt myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:17.87,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't run away and \Nstay apart any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.92,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to better myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.68,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,and stay by Miketsukami's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.93,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What did you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:33.45,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,S-Since I don't know what my \Nfuture self will be like,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:36.08,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote down some goals for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:37.39,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.93,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,We have no way to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.49,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.18,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Kotarou,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.13,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,you came here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.31,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:50.65,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get that post?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:55.08,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,So you also have some words that you'd \Nlike to leave in the time capsule?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.84,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,How sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:00.91,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm writing a letter to you, in your next life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:04.05,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:07.43,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Will I really be myself in my next life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:12.17,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can't write a letter to \Nsome old man you've never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.53,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,People become themselves \Nthrough their encounters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:20.68,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,With different things, people, and emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:25.06,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,A me who has not met your \Nmother or you is not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.44,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Was that too romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:31.44,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.29,Default,Kotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're the only dad I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:40.46,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is this happily ever after?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:42.49,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking so smug?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.55,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You knew something again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:47.08,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Could you actually be kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.89,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:51.18,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I was a bit worried because I \Ndidn't know what you were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.04,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're mistaking meddling for kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.81,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be sure, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:10:59.38,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:02.08,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.43,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Who instigated this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.39,Default,Maid2,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.20,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.06,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:09.81,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.60,Default,Maid2,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.73,Default,Maid2,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do the time sale, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.94,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,It's a time capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.16,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,You leave a message,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:24.29,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,within a durable box, \Nfor someone in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.42,Default,Maid2,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite a knowledgeable tranny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.41,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,You really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:33.79,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you've dug the hole, \NI suppose it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.46,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Just be sure you cover it back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.46,Default,Maid2,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:41.38,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,I think we have all of them now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.40,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.28,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Miketsukami wanted to add something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.75,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Ririchiyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.56,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,are you sure this is the letter \Nyou meant to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:55.36,Sign12D,Text,0000,0000,0000,,To Miketsukami
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.00,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to give it to Miketsukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.36,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want to include it \Nwith the box of cakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:12:00.01,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Could you have put the time capsule \Nletter in the other box?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:01.90,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:03.82,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's in that letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:07.63,Inuboku-internal,Text,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't run away and \Nstay apart any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:09.33,Sign12B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"But I won't run away and \Nstay apart any longer. \N\NI want to better myself."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.33,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to better myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.96,Sign12B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"And stay by \NMiketsukami's side."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.94,Inuboku-internal,Text,0000,0000,0000,,And stay by Miketsukami's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.69,Default,bubble,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.71,Sign12B,bubble,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:17.63,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.57,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ririchiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:22.18,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like you to lose your composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.06,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible he hasn't read the letter yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:26.89,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:29.90,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the speed of a novice anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:31.64,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:32.98,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Do not read that letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:37.94,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.68,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:15.29,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this have to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:19.90,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I can guess what you wrote...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.47,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,But it's obvious you both feel \Nthe same way, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.81,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Why get all worked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:27.04,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, as your big brother, \NI feel a bit lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.51,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,But does he feel the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.57,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible Sou's feelings are \Nmerely based on respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:34.27,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,He {\i1}is{\i0} seven years your senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:38.02,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,But that man isn't the type to \Nhave moral issues with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.63,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:40.39,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.60,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's a lolicon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.71,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect label for that stupid fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.53,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't get so depressed about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:51.31,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,If we hang around here, \Nhe'll join us soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.22,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mentally prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.24,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on a journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:57.77,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:05.28,Sign12E,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(446,1)}And presently...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.66,Default - Margin,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:03.26,Default - Margin,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's as if I confessed to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:05.28,Default - Margin,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't want to do that at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:09.83,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:13.06,Sign12E,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Her everyday, uncontrollable bad mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.77,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:13.05,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:16.33,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, I act precisely \Nin the opposite manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.85,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like I wanted to be his girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.27,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,or anything silly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:25.34,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just grateful to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.11,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.89,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me the courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:35.05,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to grow into a better me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:38.49,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,and give a little back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:41.27,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.98,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I turned off my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:47.03,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,The least I can do is make sure \NI can tell him I'm safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.63,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I'm effectively \Nsabotaging his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.83,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It rang the second I turned it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.66,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I haven't even devised a strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:04.42,Sign12G,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,225)}\N\N\N\NPlan One: \NThe Blitz
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:01.61,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, so don't bother looking for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:01.58,Sign12C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}Click
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.05,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Too suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.42,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,The root problem must be addressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:11.93,Sign12G,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,185)}\N\N\N\NPlan Two: \NJust Explain Yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:07.16,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That letter has no deeper meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:10.47,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You were unable to reach me until \Nnow due to bad reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.97,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Reeks of justification. Sounds like a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.90,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:18.06,Sign12G,Text,0000,0000,0000,,\N\N\N\NPlan Three: \NPretend Nothing Happened
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:15.26,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it really doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.91,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I wanted to discuss something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.06,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:21.68,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have to answer, \Nor the call will get dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:24.23,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to explain, as naturally as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.53,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That letter doesn't have a deeper meaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:27.63,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Ririch—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:31.60,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I was just looking for a long-term \Ncontractual partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:32.52,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.74,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you where you are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.05,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at Seijou Park! So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:41.25,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I don't have any special \Nfeelings toward you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:41.98,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:42.96,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I know that quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.37,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:46.19,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:47.62,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.53,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Even I thought that was an obvious excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:51.88,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.30,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:56.41,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You've told me so quite plainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:59.93,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And I am not that shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.89,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I do try to be aware of my position,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:07.02,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,my nature, my standing, how I got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:10.97,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I am someone who has done things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.93,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,that you ought never to hear of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.92,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,For me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:19.86,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,simply being by your side makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:25.52,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You actually write letters and \Ne-mails to the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.67,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot fathom how much that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.96,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I can imagine no higher form of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.39,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.76,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That is how
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.95,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I sing praises of you, as if you were sacred,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:37.94,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,while I indulge in my own fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:42.10,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I wish for no further happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.73,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Imagination is free, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.04,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.52,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the kind of man I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:52.70,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I do see, Miketsukami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:56.37,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You hate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:59.21,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I think I always knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:02.95,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Because you always slight yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:06.33,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Because your eyes seem so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.46,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Because you seem lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.75,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.01,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I understand you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:15.04,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.77,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But I was able to wish to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:20.22,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,By falling in love with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.98,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I gained that courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.62,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:37.16,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.54,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.85,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But up to now, I've hurt many others,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.33,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,all to protect myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:52.16,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, if it will give you \Neven a tiny bit of courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:55.14,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind getting hurt this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.13,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:02.99,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Even... Even if you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.52,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,cannot love yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:06.14,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:07.87,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:07.87,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Ri—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:09.87,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.04,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.68,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:25.66,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:26.78,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:28.83,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.74,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo, I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.66,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:38.51,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.51,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:46.71,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,my words were able to help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:47.95,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I truly am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:51.48,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,There is no happier feeling than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:58.37,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Look, those grown-ups are doing pervy stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:18:59.95,Default,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.63,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're staring at us, M-Mike...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:03.62,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.41,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't sniff me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:09.01,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It'll corrupt these children!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:10.13,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's separate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:13.44,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo, this is like a dream to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.96,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?! Let go—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.65,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,When I got that letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:21.34,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself that I must not misunderstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:25.26,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I'd have lost my composure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.06,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:32.63,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy, I could have died...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:41.74,Title1E12,Title,0000,0000,0000,,The Day We Came Together
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.00,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Want to get ice cream at the concession stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:51.68,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you eating right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:53.44,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,This is soft serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:57.13,Default - Margin,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, you human toilets!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.51,Default - Margin,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for the girls, \Nthey went to a camp by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:00.76,Default - Margin,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Abandonment play, sadistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.60,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I found you, you worms...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.26,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you could run from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.80,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,It's Master Kage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:12.10,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.61,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,All right, come on over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:15.44,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,You want to join us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:18.23,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Cut up that squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:23.07,Default - Margin,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,Ririchiyo, I'll put sunscreen on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:24.91,Sign12F,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Blue School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:24.91,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Cross-dresser, incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:28.20,Default - Margin,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,It's the old standby, "boy dressed as girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.95,Default - Margin,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki, you look quite cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:34.13,Default - Margin,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,How did your exams turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.63,Default - Margin,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can say that, thanks to everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.05,Default - Margin,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,my score was just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:42.38,Default - Margin,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,They took away my candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:44.88,Default - Margin,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Where shall we go today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:46.06,Default - Margin,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:49.25,Default - Margin,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You look great in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:51.52,Default - Margin,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.89,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Miketsukami...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:55.92,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I need to use your restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.06,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:05.59,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:10.20,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You did say that you loved me \Nthe way I am, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.00,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know this was the real you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:46.83,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:51.31,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I have only one dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.58,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.12,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:56.83,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:22:01.81,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It can be a superficial lie, \Nexisting only right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:06.05,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo, I want a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:09.39,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I want a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:11.30,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.26,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.26,0:22:20.18,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,in your childhood that I'd never seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:22.04,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:24.34,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:29.32,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You were lonely, and you were precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:31.65,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:37.79,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to answer \Non the spur of the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:40.21,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:43.00,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:44.77,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:47.51,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:52.15,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take plenty of time, \Nand think it over together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.62,0:22:57.51,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Time is a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:00.00,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.55,0:23:04.19,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,The time you have lived thus far...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:10.26,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,The time you have lived thus far...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.63,0:23:16.70,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,We'll remember it, again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:20.49,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,The story of a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:24.13,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,The story of a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:28.82,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,long, long time we'll live out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:41.89,Next timeE12,Text,0000,0000,0000,,And the story moves from spring to summer...
